94
00:05:00,100 --> 00:05:00,960
Alright, Lici.

95
00:05:01,790 --> 00:05:03,190
If we don't practice now,

96
00:05:03,420 --> 00:05:04,620
they'll be back soon.

97
00:05:05,350 --> 00:05:12,370
♪ Yearn for what's yearnable,
